import React from 'react'
import { Row,Container,Col } from 'react-bootstrap'
import { SeccionImagen } from './SeccionImagen'
const ContenedorGrids = () => {
  return ( 
        <section className='imgCont '>
            <Container fluid>
                <Col>
                    <Row>
                        <SeccionImagen/>
                    </Row>
                </Col>
            </Container>
        </section> 
  )
}

export default ContenedorGrids
